Name: S.T.A.R Space Typing Action Rangers
About the game: This game teaches the traditional way of typing called, 'Touch Typing'. It is a space themed game that will teach you proper finger placement and usage. There are three levels. The first level teaches you where the home keys are located and which finger to use depending on the key that is highlighted. The second level will test the skills of the first level with a challenging objective. Finally, when the third level unlocks, you will have 3 options to choose from and test your your typing skills with tracked accuracy and words per minute.
